parameters:
Fake adventurer Psema (Ugh... my body hurts... but it seems
like the bleeding has stopped...)

Fake adventurer Psema (Heheh, it seems like I was saved by a
kind person. The paralysis from the fake death potion should
wear off soon...)
Fake adventurer Psema (For now, my body--)
後SE：鎖のジャリジャリした音
Fake adventurer Psema: W-What is this!?
Stolge the Merciful: Hey, how are your injuries?

Fake adventurer Psema: Y-You guys are from the Adventurer's
Guild...!?

Guild Master Agonia: Nice to meet you, Psema-san. I have
heard the rumors that you have been spreading about our
guild.

Guild Master Agonia: As a token of our gratitude, we have
invited you to a special room today. This is a place that
even Clea and Celis, who have taken care of you, are not
familiar with.

Simos of the Unknown Night: Start right away! It's tiring to
hold back from killing this guy!

Stolge the Merciful: Do you understand this? It seems Nora
picked it up. It appears to be a staff with brainwashing
effects.

Stolge the Merciful: You're lucky there was no torture.
Well, you should know what awaits you after we extract the
information.
後SE：鎖のジャリジャリした音

Fake adventurer Psema: H-Hey! Let's make a deal, please,
I'll cooperate with you!
後ACT：プセマが邪悪なオーラに包まれる（時間経過後も継続）
Fake adventurer Psema: Ahh, m-my consciousness, ughhh...!

Fake adventurer Psema: I have been cooperating mainly with
the Queen's faction, especially in the operation to
exterminate the thieves in Camps. I was the one who incited
it.
Guild Master Agonia: What is the reason?

Fake adventurer Psema: The most important thing is that they
started trading the drugs I distributed without permission,
and Eratoma requested a large number of corpses.
Guild Master Agonia: Why did they need the corpses?

Fake adventurer Psema: The man named Eratoma said it was
dragon material.
Stolge the Merciful: Was Clea's report not wrong...

Guild Master Agonia: You were also cooperating with the
Prince's faction, weren't you?

Fake adventurer Psema: I cooperated with Pido from the
Senate and intervened in both factions. I also obtained the
Dillark's staff that they are using with information from
the Prince's faction.

Guild Master Agonia: ...What information did Melos sell to
you?

Fake adventurer Psema: It's just the transportation route of
the giant crystal. It was my strategy to use that and incite
distrust.

Fake adventurer Psema: He repeatedly refused, and there was
no one else who didn't break down like him.

Guild Master Agonia: This is the final question. Can we
obtain medicine to treat Ect's illness?

Fake adventurer Psema: We no longer have any stock. That was
a lost technology manufactured in the old academy.

Fake adventurer Psema: ...Huh?! Y-You guys, there's still a
lot more to it!

Fake adventurer Psema: You should know my abilities! I'll
join the Adventurer's Guild and swear loyalty to all of you!

Guild Master Agonia: I won't betray you, I won't lie, and I
won't run away.

Guild Master Agonia: You are the furthest thing from an
adventurer.

Stolge the Merciful: Shimos, can you finish him off in one
strike? Just the fact that this guy is still alive is
unpleasant.

Shimos of the Unknown Night: It's not something that
benevolence should say... but I agree.

Fake adventurer Psema: W-Wait, please! I'll do anything,
just don't leave me here like this!

Shimos of the Unknown Night: If you're willing to do
anything, then I have one request. I don't think you can go
to the same place as Melos, but...

Shimos of the Unknown Night: If you see him... tell him I
avenged him and to treat me to a drink!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
実績 洗脳と暴風と決着
